---
import Eyebrow from "./ui/Eyebrow.astro";
---

<section id="why">
  <div class="wrap">
    <Eyebrow>Why it's different</Eyebrow>
    <h2>Quiet command, not coverage.</h2>
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="reveal">
        <h3>Self-contained</h3>
        <p>Zero external links inside the skill. The agent loads only the file a task needs, and the answer is right there.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <h3>Tradeoff-first</h3>
        <p>No option is named without the constraint it fits and the cost it carries. A design with no stated tradeoff isn't finished.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <h3>License-clean</h3>
        <p>Original prose, inspired by the taxonomy of <em>System Design 101</em> but never copied from it. MIT.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <h3>Works offline</h3>
        <p>Plain Markdown and two JSON manifests. No build, no runtime, no network. Install and go.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
